headline: The Smartest Dividend Stocks to Buy With $100 Right Now
summary: Realty Income has raised its dividend payment 131 times since it went public.  Invitation Homes has increased its dividend every year since its initial public offering.  Rexford Industrial Realty has boosted its payout by nearly 250% over the past decade.
